President of the Senate, Ahmad Lawan, and other political heavy weights, on Saturday attended the wedding Fatiha of Kaduna State Governor’s son, Bashir Nasir El-Rufai and Halima Ibrahim Kazaure, which held in Abuja. Bashir and his bride, Halima tied the knot in an exquisite wedding which was attended by so many dignitaries. Also in attendance was the Governor of Jigawa State, Alhaji Badaru Abubakar; Yobe State Governor, Mai Mala Buni, and a former Emir of Kano, Muhammadu Sanusi II. See pictures below…<img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-855846" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/wedding3.jpg.webp" alt="" width="1172" height="776" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/wedding3.jpg.webp 1172w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/wedding3-300x199.jpg.webp 300w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/wedding3-1024x678.jpg.webp 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1172px) 100vw, 1172px"> <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-855847" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/wedding2.jpg.webp" alt="" width="1162" height="738" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/wedding2.jpg.webp 1162w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/wedding2-300x191.jpg.webp 300w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/wedding2-1024x650.jpg.webp 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1162px) 100vw, 1162px"> <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-855848" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/wedding1.jpg.webp" alt="" width="1133" height="758" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/wedding1.jpg.webp 1133w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/wedding1-300x201.jpg.webp 300w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/wedding1-1024x685.jpg.webp 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1133px) 100vw, 1133px">